// credential vends, auth decisions) — even when NO audit-log plugin is installed
// (it falls back to a core-local append-only store). "audit-log: none" must NOT
// mean "no audit". This plugin axis decides WHERE the trail goes, never WHETHER
// it exists. That is why audit is in the core's enforcement layer
